        %p Tom Callahan joined Vantage Partners in 2006 and is responsible for the Technology Practice at the firm.  Tom established his eye for engineering talent at Oracle Corporation, where he spearheaded its technical recruiting for eight years and partnered closely with senior executives handling their strategic hiring and planning initiatives during the company's expansion from a $5 billion to $10 Billion software giant.  
